<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2011/08/nuspec.xsd">
    <metadata>
        <id>{{PackageName}}</id>
        <version>{{PackageVersion}}</version>
        <title>pdfFactory Pro Workstation</title>
        <authors>Fineprint Software</authors>
        <projectUrl>http://fineprint.com/pdfp/</projectUrl>
        <iconUrl>http://fineprint.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/fineprint/images/pdfp.png</iconUrl>
        <description>Easy, reliable PDF creation from all applications.
        
You can pass the following parameters:

* UI language: `/lang:&lt;language>`
* License code: `/license:&lt;your license code>`
* Name of the license holder - this is ignored if no license code has been specified: `/name:"&lt;your name>"`
* Printer margins in 1/100th of an inch: `/margins:"&lt;top> &lt;right> &lt;bottom> &lt;left>"`
        
Available languages are:

* Chinese (Simplified): `zh-CN`
* Chinese (Traditional): `zh-TW`
* Czech: `cs`
* Danish: `da`
* Dutch: `nl`
* English: `en`
* French: `fr`
* German: `de`
* Italian: `it`
* Japanese: `ja`
* Polish: `pl`
* Portuguese: `pt`
* Russian: `ru`
* Slovak: `sk`
* Spanish: `es`
* Swedish: `sv`


Example:  

`-params '/lang:en /license:ABCDE-12345-FGHIJ /name:""John Doe"" /margins:""0 0 0 0""'`
        
NOTE: This package installs a printer driver. If you have UAC prompts enabled, you will need to confirm the driver installation.</description>
        <language>en-US</language>
        <tags>PDF printing letterhead</tags>
    </metadata>
    <files>
        <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
        <file src="..\..\..\..\extensions.ps1" target="tools" />
    </files>
</package>